divs: Sighting DetailsThis happened 2 days in a row between 11:30 and 12:00 the October 2nd and 3rd. I never sighted anything but it made a high pitched squeal varying in pitch and noise level. it was high pitched enough to almost hurt the ears. My son and I rushed outside but could not see anything. The 2 dogs I have jumped off the couch and rubbed their ears on the carpet.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Pine Island
This sighting has never been favorited.
